Package org.opensextant.giscore.output.shapefile

Class ShapefileBaseClass

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.output.StreamVisitorBase
org.opensextant.giscore.output.shapefile.ShapefileBaseClass
All Implemented Interfaces:
IStreamVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ShapefileOutputStream, SingleShapefileOutputHandler
public abstract class ShapefileBaseClass extends StreamVisitorBase
Common methods and constants for use with both input and output of shapefiles as GIS objects. Values copied from ShpHandler in transfusion's mediate package.
